{"pin":"BH00074","subcodes":[{"code":"BH00074","anchor":"","first_line":"Praised be God Who hath manifested through the influence of His Most Exalted Pen unto all who dwell in the kingdom of creation, whereupon every weary one hath spoken [3.5s]... ...Let not the happenings of the world sadden you. I swear by God! The sea of joy yearneth… Blessed is the spot, and the house… Regarding what ye had written as to the Mashriqu’l-Adhkár’s having been established… It is the binding command of God that in every locality whatever hath been or will be made available for the Ḥuqúqu’lláh should be submitted to His Holy Presence","first_line_orig":"الحمد لله الذی تجلی باثر قلمه الاعلی علی من فی ملکوت الانشاء اذا نطق کل کلیل  ","language":"5","word_count":"4990","subjects":"@firmness in the Covenant, @steadfastness; perseverance; faithfulness, @unity; oneness of humanity, @service to others; to the Cause of God, @teaching the Cause; call to teach, @House of Worship [Mashriqu'l-Adhkar], @the Word of God; influence and centrality of, @power of the Manifestation of God","translations":[{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"}]},{"code":"BH00074BLE","anchor":"ble","translations":[{"language":"oj","lang_name":"Ojibwe"},{"language":"gwi","lang_name":"Gwich'in"},{"language":"eu","lang_name":"Basque"},{"language":"lt","lang_name":"Lithuanian"},{"language":"ny","lang_name":"Chichewa"},{"language":"fy","lang_name":"Western Frisian"},{"language":"hur","lang_name":"Halkomelem"},{"language":"bla","lang_name":"Blackfoot"},{"language":"sr","lang_name":"Serbian"},{"language":"ik","lang_name":"Inupiaq"},{"language":"chr","lang_name":"Cherokee"},{"language":"no","lang_name":"Norwegian"},{"language":"be","lang_name":"Belarusian"},{"language":"kiw","lang_name":"Kiwai"},{"language":"sm","lang_name":"Samoan"},{"language":"slh","lang_name":"Sliammon"},{"language":"dgz","lang_name":"Daga"},{"language":"ga","lang_name":"Irish"},{"language":"lut","lang_name":"Lushootseed"},{"language":"haw","lang_name":"Ha